{"id":39842,"date":"2024-02-04T09:37:00","date_gmt":"2022-12-04T04:07:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=39842"},"modified":"2024-11-05T13:31:20","modified_gmt":"2024-11-05T08:01:20","slug":"lounge-chairs-for-living-room","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/lounge-chairs-for-living-room\/","title":{"rendered":"Living Room Lounge Chair Ideas To Revive The Lost Art Of Unwinding"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Sit back and relax in these comfy lounge chairs for the living room. Take your pick from our designs!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Lounge chairs<\/strong> are not a staple for home interiors but when you look for a nook to unwind after a stressful day with a much-needed drink or to read a book on a rainy day by the window while sipping a hot cup of tea, lounge chairs become essential.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Set it up in a corner creating a reading nook or keep it by the couches as additional seating \u2014 these versatile lounge chairs can elevate the style of your living room in a jiffy. All that is left is for you to sit, put your feet up, and relax. Here are some amazing <strong>living room lounge chair<\/strong> design ideas for you to consider.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Highback Lounge Chair In The Living Room Is A Reading Nook Staple<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/reading-nook\/\">reading nook<\/a> is incomplete without a wingback lounge chair. This beige chair fills the awkward gap in the corner of the living room beautifully. The textured cotton fabric of the chair makes it eco-friendly and feels oh so good. A curved metal floor lamp and oversized picture frame complete the reading nook perfectly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124420\/highback-lounge-chair-for-living-room-india.jpg\" alt=\"Beige highback lounge chair for living room in India\" class=\"wp-image-39843\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124420\/highback-lounge-chair-for-living-room-india.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124420\/highback-lounge-chair-for-living-room-india-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124420\/highback-lounge-chair-for-living-room-india-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124420\/highback-lounge-chair-for-living-room-india-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A highback modern lounge chair for the living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Lounge Chairs In The Living Room Offer Extra Seating<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This <strong>grey lounge chair<\/strong> effortlessly balances the moody vibe of this living room. The red velvet couch with dark grey walls and golden accent pieces strategically placed all across the space gives a mysterious look. So, the light grey lounge chair may seem like a misfit, but it is essential to add the much-needed balance. Also, it works perfectly as additional seating at a perfect angle to watch TV and continue the conversation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124445\/modern-lounge-chairs-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Modern lounge chair for living room with shapely curves\" class=\"wp-image-39847\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124445\/modern-lounge-chairs-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124445\/modern-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124445\/modern-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124445\/modern-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern living room lounge chair with shapely curves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dramatic Wingback Lounge Chair In A Minimalist Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This powder blue wingback chair is one of the proud possessions of the owner of this apartment. The chair goes well with the general white and blue combination of the interior. The black and white striped pouffe works as a footstool for a comfortable conversation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124450\/wingback-lounge-chair-for-minimalist-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Blue wingback lounge chair in minimalist living room\" class=\"wp-image-39848\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124450\/wingback-lounge-chair-for-minimalist-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124450\/wingback-lounge-chair-for-minimalist-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124450\/wingback-lounge-chair-for-minimalist-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124450\/wingback-lounge-chair-for-minimalist-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A wingback comfy lounge chair for the living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to make your living room fun and quirky\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09102959\/want-to-make-your-living-room-fun-and-quirky.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Leather Lounge Chair For The Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wall-to-wall bookshelf with more hidden compartments, a <strong>comfy lounge chair<\/strong> in tan leather, a black marble top side table and a reading <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/floor-lamp-ideas\/\">floor lamp<\/a> \u2013 this nook of the living room is a bookworm\u2019s paradise. With just the right amount of curves and cushions, this tan lounge chair is the definition of the lost art of unwinding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124427\/leather-lounge-chairs-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Brown leather lounge chair for living room\" class=\"wp-image-39844\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124427\/leather-lounge-chairs-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124427\/leather-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124427\/leather-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124427\/leather-lounge-chairs-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Comfy lounge chair in tan leather for some reading<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mid-Century Modern Wooden Lounge Chair For The Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If there\u2019s any interior design style that proves its presence without being too loud and flashy, it is mid-century modern. It is the epitome of simplicity and chicness. So, it is not surprising to witness how this glossy black <strong>wooden lounge chair<\/strong> creates drama against the ruby red wall and contrasting light wood chest of drawers. This nook looks like a picture out of an architectural magazine, doesn\u2019t it?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124438\/mid-century-wooden-lounge-chair-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Mid-century wooden lounge chair in living room is the epitome of simplicity and chicness\" class=\"wp-image-39846\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124438\/mid-century-wooden-lounge-chair-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124438\/mid-century-wooden-lounge-chair-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124438\/mid-century-wooden-lounge-chair-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/02124438\/mid-century-wooden-lounge-chair-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden lounge chair for the living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>How did you like these living room lounge chair designs? Aren\u2019t they lovely? If you, too, want to incorporate a living room lounge chair in your home and give it an instant upgrade, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">reach out to our designers<\/a> today. For more living room design ideas, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/\">blog section<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">design gallery<\/a>.<br><br>Also, Check Out\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/lounge-chairs-for-living-room\/\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\